{"tid":1561063,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［置頂] 九月十五號呀！","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:52.000Z","uid":211578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b011a8d7e0a678ca51d061d0fd11801b632e7af","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"大家唔好掛住沉醉係琴晚一齊唱國歌<br />\n點解熱門可以一個post都冇？<br />\n同我推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">九月十五號<br />\n下午三點 民陣大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n全部人同我出嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要喺銅鑼灣見到你地！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4wparw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4wparw.jpg&h=a6dd03fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBx0tdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBx0tdc.jpg&h=7960907a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5p368dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5p368dd.jpg&h=4d5d3b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVH0tde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVH0tde.jpg&h=a679fd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5c7aff90f149909475ad6aa40ef42931e71d3a5","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6d74b76dd53994de0cdbd307c8e5c0cae1b9c51","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"076479b59b8bc3dc1e448121d5e4a378ef00a348","tid":1561063,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"建議為區選選區，尤其反自動當選的，各區獨立設一個台<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 既然冇大台提供可靠懶人包結論，就要期望唔少唔多喜歡睇文字的手足認真閱讀分析 &quot;raw material&quot; ．每台只處理跟各人相關的資料，可以方便大家作出明智決定，亦方便 admin 管理（移動錯台post／垃圾文 etc）<br />\n2. 這兩天有關 歐頌賢 及 任嘉兒 的討論，大家要跟post都已經有Ｄ難度，遲下區多人多時間逼，再加大大班臥底時，肯定亂到九彩，早日作好安排好Ｄ．"},{"pid":"157462560b666548c72da8b4d2cd59a92c5925bb","tid":1561063,"uid":65503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3f144bb5d84e4a7bdfc7e94fda23ed9adfd572bd","tid":1561063,"uid":208253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"【 五大訴求，缺一不可 】遊行公佈<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在日前正式宣佈撤回引渡條例，在立法會復會後，以不需表決的方式完全撤回引渡條例。有外國的朋友甚至對香港人致以「祝賀」，但緊接的周末，港人的抗爭依然不斷。<br />\n<br />\n因為我們知道，勝利仍未來臨。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭的撤回引渡條例修訂，僅是以退為進，將一條已死的條文再一次加以埋葬，自以為將風暴的起源堵上，風暴就會平息，就可以名正言順地污名化香港人的持續抗爭。我們要求正式撤回條例，並不是單純在行政程序上撤回，而是我們所追求的是一個負責任、會聆聽民意、會尊重民意的政府，因此我們不會接受一個為了自身一人的面子，玩弄文字，無視程序的政府管治。數月來，政府、警隊醜態原形畢露，林鄭想以虛假的「四大公關SHOW」回應五大訴求，簡直天荒夜談。<br />\n<br />\n在惡法撤回之後，我們必須清晰告訴世界，我們之所以繼續抗爭，是因為我們仍有四個訴求未被回應，而餘下的四個訴求，是彰顯我們對社會願景的原則，反映我們對生活的城市的愛，並且正面迎戰我們不能忍受的醜惡政權的種種惡行。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受，警員濫暴濫權，變成持有合法武力的黑社會，而沒有任何獨立監察的制度可以制衡；<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受，守住香港，擋住惡法的年輕人一個又一個因為捨身行動而失去自由，被指控發動暴動，被指稱為暴徒、曱甴；<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受，我們的家人、朋友，每一個心愛的人生活在荒誕的極權的謊言之中，而我們手中沒有任何權力、選票可以與之抗衡；<br />\n<br />\n我們不能忍受以上種種，因此，為我們愛的城市，為了我們身邊的每一個人，我們會繼續抗爭，行使我們相信的方法繼續抗爭，直至五大訴求得到落實；直至我們心中公義、民主的社會來臨為止。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心。<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊遊行詳情＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月15日<br />\n下午2時30分<br />\n銅鑼灣東角道集合<br />\n遊行往中環遮打道<br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年9月11日"},{"pid":"c6f1b7bacfb54314ecb2bb8d86b49e80e547e1ad","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"915 民陣大遊行"},{"pid":"446138e55ff152f06a35da86867a3d16f2d6f903","tid":1561063,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"81627139bfd3ff06f4e01c18d2b9b8915c7afaff","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"f9129be71c386c077f2d755cd89953e9c3e4f559","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"744e015d30f67eaa730b0c0d7d050ae7cabfb44f","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"af421eabbe24e8610b66ce5ec1990c121196a05e","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"132c1e6dfa74d7479fa7751676f2fc817d19f149","tid":1561063,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"究竟係2半定3？"},{"pid":"e99abaeb38c4a4b9aa9daa4b748fd7efc6805d7f","tid":1561063,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩未食飯既同我入哂黎!!! 唔準有人餓住個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"499cfd535d353c88a833f5975f8fe1c46b05ab0b","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC9Vg9X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC9Vg9X.jpg&h=7019a454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同行兒女為正義 時代革命！！"},{"pid":"f8ca628e2132aba59f516a2cbd0eb99d1a90b0c4","tid":1561063,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7566cbb8325a2d246adb474f0859a56ba531d53","tid":1561063,"uid":295795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"推"}]}